*"U sekunde* se začuo trzaj.", (In a second a jolt was heard.)

*"Izmerio je vreme u sekundama*.", (He measured time in seconds.)

*"Bio je gotov za nekoliko sekundi*.", (He was done in a few seconds.)

*"Vreme je isteklo u roku od sekunde*.", (Time expired within a second.)

*"Misli se premeštaju brže od sekunde*.", (Thoughts move faster than a second.)

*"Koraci su se čuli u sekundi*.", (Steps were heard in a second.)